title: AOMEI Partition Assistant 6.0 All Edition 2016
description:
AOMEI Partition Assistant 6.0 STD/Professional/Server/Technician/Unlimited.

is an easy to use all-in-one Hard Disk Partition Software. It offers various free partition management features 
for both all home users and commercial users. AOMEI Partition Assistant Standard is the right one for your PC, 
guaranteeing you get the full features for creating, resizing, moving, copying, deleting, wiping, aligning, formating, 
merging, splitting partition and more. AOMEI partition manager enables you to extend the available space on hard disk quickly 
for improve the capacity for the original partition. The smart migration wizard could easily assist you to migrate OS to 
another hard disk including SSD and HDD. Built-in step by step wizards realize you to easily finish complex operations 
including copying partition, cloning entire hard disk
